      <title>加拿大的卡尼将保持关税，直到美国承诺自由贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/canada-s-carney-will-keep-tariffs-until-us-commits-to-free-trade-m84tlznf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）表示，加拿大将保持其贸易报复，直到美国取消自己的关税并承诺自由贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/canada-s-carney-will-keep-tariffs-until-us-commits-to-free-trade-m84tlznf</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 18:24:27 GMT</pubDate>
